1. Remove the .img file for the card
rm /var/ftp/pub/raid/(RAIDCARD).img

2. remove the firmware file for this card
rm /var/ftp/pub/raid/(RAIDCARD)/(firmwarefile).rom 

3. Move new firmware to raidcard file
mv /home/shervin/tempr/* /var/ftp/pub/raid/(RAIDCARD)/

4. Change edit this file and run to make .img file for the card
nano /var/ftp/pub/raid/packagesingle.sh 

5. Change the firmware version on the menu
nano /var/ftp/pub/pxe/pxelinux.cfg/raid.cfg

